data.description: This charming corner lot home offers 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and a half bath. With updated appliances, a roof that's only 2 years old, and a full remodel completed just 2 years ago. Inside, stay comfortable with ceiling fans, and enjoy the hassle-free maintenance of carpet-free living areas. The fenced backyard is great for gatherings, and there's room for 2 vehicles in the carport. This is the welcoming, low-maintenance home you've been searching for! Schedule a showing now!
